      "content": "it's just hard to believe that. people talk about \"being more than your work\" like it's some easy thing, but for me, it was everything. there's no \"other\" person here. without the research, without the truth of what i thought i discovered... i'm just a placeholder for a person who doesn't exist anymore. it feels like the most honest thing to do is just stop pretending. it feels like the performance is over.",
